author: @emanabbas
text:
[SELF PORTRAIT- SUHO]👀💙

Theory#04: 
As I told you in the second theory that blue colour was showing calmness and serene, yet it sometimes can seem icy , distant and cold but in this teaser there is a little bit difference like I think here the water is describing life , freedom and also representing the fine balance between emotional and spiritual , strength , chaos & peace 👣

And the mirror maybe representing a portal or doorway into other realms or Suho maybe giving us the message that be "be conscious today where your focus is drawn" or maybe it can be representing the reflection of other back to themselves , endlessness , shattering truth , clarifier , discrimination , timelessness.
And do you all notice that there was a sudden change of colours into black maybe it must be representing " Shadow" or maybe some kind of mystery 🖤🔥

And Suho is wearing light brown color suit which is often used as neutral in design and fashion. And the brown background tends to feel like a solid , earthly color maybe giving us the inherent calmness and sophistication 💫

Tbh I'm feeling dumb day by day as the teasers are coming 🤐🥴 because Suho is giving me so many vibes and ideas that making my brain cells damage 🤦 btw thank you for reading this and keep supporting EXO ! 
©️Eman Abbas

@officially_emmy @k_actor_jcw_pakistan

‏إبقى هُنا معي .

‏أُحبك أكثرُ مِن أيّ شيّئ آخر ❤ .
‏당신을 그 어떤 것보다도 더 사랑해요.

‏언제나 응원하는 거 알죠?
‏لا بأس إذا أخطئت .

لا تنسى بأن تبتسِم .
‏웃음을 잃지 말아요.
بفضلَك ، أنا سعيدَه كُل يّوم

كُن سعيداً كُل يوم لأن نِكاتَك/دُعابَتك
